184
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:08,080
The title is "The Political Problems of Today's China"

185
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:11,520
Consider it a public declaration that I, Chen Duxiu,

186
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:14,320
will no longer abide by my promise to not discuss politics for twenty years.

187
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:15,840
I've broken my vow.

188
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:16,560
The essay

189
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:18,240
will be published in this issue of "New Youth."

190
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:20,800
