212
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:09,920
we want to set up other newspapers and periodicals.

213
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:11,200
The second,

214
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:14,240
I will personally establish a Society for Advancing Morality.

215
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:16,960
"Great learning makes a teacher, and moral integrity makes a model."

216
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:18,640
