220
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,920
I fully approve.

221
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:34,720
Great. Great.

222
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:35,760
Very good, very good.

223
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:37,840
