667
00:29:10,320 --> 00:29:11,440
Brother Jiemin, what-

668
00:29:11,920 --> 00:29:12,960
What are you doing?

669
00:29:13,280 --> 00:29:14,240
What are you doing here?

670
00:29:14,320 --> 00:29:15,200
I... I...

671
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:18,480
You can't stay up so late.

672
00:29:18,880 --> 00:29:19,920
I'm rushing for a story.

673
00:29:21,440 --> 00:29:22,400
Brother Jiemin, wait for me.

674
00:29:22,560 --> 00:29:23,120
I'll wash my face.

675
00:29:23,360 --> 00:29:24,320
Never mind, never mind.

676
00:29:24,640 --> 00:29:25,600
Hurry home and wash.

677
00:29:26,080 --> 00:29:27,360
Go home, wash up and sleep.

678
00:29:27,840 --> 00:29:28,480
Today's sunny,

679
00:29:28,640 --> 00:29:29,680
what home am I going to?

680
00:29:29,760 --> 00:29:29,920
No!

681
00:29:30,160 --> 00:29:32,080
You go home, you take today off.

682
00:29:32,400 --> 00:29:33,280
Take a day off.

683
00:29:34,320 --> 00:29:35,680
I'm not going back. I have a lot of things to do.

684
00:29:36,480 --> 00:29:37,760
Go back when I tell you to.

685
00:29:38,160 --> 00:29:39,440
You have to listen to what I say.

686
00:29:39,680 --> 00:29:40,480
From now on,

687
00:29:40,720 --> 00:29:42,800
